wiki.content: B.o.B described this cut during a listening session interview with Mack of Sound-Savvy as a, "victory lap song with a big sound that a lot of people will gravitate towards." (Source So Good Songfacts) The six time Grammy nominated rapper/songwriter is touring the UK in September 2012. “So Good” reached No.7 in the UK singles chart in April 2012, making it B.o.B's third top 10 single.
